        "respondWith": "text",
        "responseBody": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-TW\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<title>發票上傳 OCR</title>\n<style>\n  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 500px; margin: 60px auto; background: #e8f8f8; }\n  .card { background: white; padding: 32px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }\n  h2 { color: #0E6B6B; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n  p  { color: #666; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 20px; }\n  label { display: block; font-weight: bold; color: #333; margin-bottom: 6px; }\n  input[type=file] { width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 2px dashed #1A9696;\n    border-radius: 6px; box-sizing: border-box; background: #EBF9F9;\n    font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; }\n  input[type=text] { width: 100%; padding: 9px 12px; border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    border-radius: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; }\n  button { width: 100%; margin-top: 18px; padding: 12px;\n    background: #0E6B6B; color: white; border: none;\n    border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; }\n  button:hover { background: #1A9696; }\n  .tip { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 6px; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"card\">\n  <h2>🧾 發票 OCR 上傳</h2>\n  <p>上傳發票圖片，系統將自動使用 AI 識別發票內容並存入記錄</p>\n  <form action=\"/webhook-test/invoice-ocr\" method=\"POST\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\">\n    <label>買方名稱（選填）</label>\n    <input type=\"text\" name=\"buyerName\" placeholder=\"王小明\">\n    <label>發票圖片</label>\n    <input type=\"file\" name=\"invoiceImage\" accept=\"image/*\" required>\n    <p class=\"tip\">支援 JPG、PNG、WEBP 格式，建議解析度 800px 以上</p>\n    <button type=\"submit\">📤 上傳並識別</button>\n  </form>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
        "options": {}
